---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section id="faq" class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Got questions...? We have all the answers!</h2>
            <div class="faq-container">
              <details>
                <summary>What is OJUBABES Matchmaking?</summary>
                <p>OJUBABES is a personalized matchmaking service designed to help you find a serious and meaningful relationship. We focus on detailed profiles and verified members to ensure a high-quality experience.</p>
              </details>
              <details>
                <summary>Is my data secure?</summary>
                <p>Absolutely. We prioritize your privacy and use secure systems to protect your information. Please read our Privacy Policy for more details.</p>
              </details>
              <details>
                <summary>How does the matching process work?</summary>
                <p>Our algorithm considers your profile, preferences, and values to suggest compatible matches. We believe in quality over quantity.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
